Get names of differential co-expression methods

Source: R/inference_methods.R
dcMethods.Rd

Returns a list of differential co-expression methods

dcMethods()

Value

names of methods implemented

Examples

dcMethods()
#>  [1] "dicer"       "diffcoex"    "ebcoexpress" "entropy"     "ftgi"       
#>  [6] "ggm-based"   "ldgm"        "magic"       "mindy"       "zscore"
